   Stock prices slumped today amid renewed worries
about the business outlook.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials dropped 11.94 to
2,749.15 by noontime on Wall Street.
   Losers outnumbered gainers by more than 2 to 1 in nationwide
trading of New York Stock Exchange-listed issues, with 453 up, 919
down and 494 unchanged.
