<FILEID>AP-NR-12-14-89 1446EST</FILEID>
<FIRST>r f AM-Allied-FederatedFinances CORRECTIVE   12-14 0075</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Allied-Federated Finances, CORRECTIVE,0077</SECOND>
<HEAD>Eds: Members who used f0315, AM-Allied-Federated Finances, sent Dec.
13 under a Cincinnati dateline, are asked to use the following story.</HEAD>
